headline: JPMorgan Chase (JPM) Valuation Check After Earnings Beat And Apple Card Portfolio Acquisition
summary: JPMorgan Chase (JPM) just paired a solid earnings update with the planned acquisition of Goldman Sachs’s Apple Card portfolio, giving investors fresh information on both current profitability and on how the credit card business could evolve.
